snippet.title: Westwood Monopoly CD-ROM Intro
snippet.description: A shortened version of the intro video of Monopoly CD-ROM board game made by Westwood Entertainment in 1995 originally for Windows 3.1/95. It works well with Windows XP too. Sadly, there are no many websites that still provide it for purchase or download...
